description.en: CubToken bridges the gap between the Web2 centralized mindset and the Web3 decentralized movement. Within the CubToken ecosystem exist a third-party strategy between a network of businesses and CubToken. The mission of our project is to expedite the bridging of this gap while maintaining the confidentiality and trust of proprietary data.
